      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and she\u2019s still got so much life left in her! It\u2019s been super reliable for me, runs like a dream, and has been really well-taken care of over the years. It\u2019s in great shape and ready for its next adventure. If you're looking for a solid, honest car that won't let you down, you\u2019ve found it! Feel free to reach out with any questions or if you want to come by and take it for a spin\u2014I'd love to see it go to a good home!",
      "price": 29500.0,
