    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sorted 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This naturally aspirated power plant utilizes individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system to deliver a 7,900 RPM redline. Power is sent to the rear wheels via a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory-spec variable M differential lock. The chassis has been maintained with technical rigor, including documented rear subframe reinforcement and a recent valve shim adjustment to ensure peak volumetric efficiency. While the exterior displays minor road-derived patina, the suspension geometry remains tight with upgraded polyurethane bushings and refreshed dampers. A high-performance specimen optimized for lateral G-loading and throttle-steer precision.",
      "price": 34800.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
