    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Up for sale is a reliable and well-presented vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between luxury and everyday utility. The exterior paint retains a brilliant luster, though a close inspection reveals minor road-pebble chips on the front bumper and a small, superficial scratch near the rear wheel well\u2014typical for a car that has been enjoyed on the open road. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and has never been smoked in; the leather seats remain supple, showing only light creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster. Every electronic feature, from the responsive touchscreen navigation to the heated seats and dual-zone climate control, functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is sound, having undergone regular synthetic oil changes and a recent brake pad replacement. The tires have plenty of tread remaining, and the transmission shifts smoothly through all gears. This is a solid, honest car that has been maintained with an open checkbook and is ready for its next owner to drive home today.",
